GateDocument.TextWithNodes: To colleagues interested in Active , Real- Time , and / or Temporal Databases : We would like to remind you that the submission deadline for the Second International Workshop on Active , Real- Time , and Temporal Database Systems , ARTDB- 97 , is approaching ( April 15 , 1997 . ) For additional information about workshop scope , submission procedures , etc . please see our WWW page .
